Craigslist,is,a,website,that,lists,classified,ads,divided,by,sections,including,jobs,housing,personals,and,more,The,Bulk,Posting,API,provides,users,with,an,interface,that,allows,for,the,submission,of,multiple,posts,in,a,single,request,Requests,must,include,a,description,a,post,category,the,city,the,post,will,be,submitted,for,and,a,reply,email,The,API,uses,HTTP,calls,and,responses,are,formatted,in,XML